---
// =============================================================================
// How It Works 页 /how-it-works —— 透明化流程，建立信任
//
// 【信任建设的核心】老外最大的顾虑是"会不会被骗""钱付了怎么办"
// 这个页面把整个流程、费用、边界讲得清清楚楚，竞品 Inside China 做得很好
// 我们做得更透明，差异化是「科技路线 + 真实可兑现」
// =============================================================================
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import ContactChannels from '../components/ContactChannels.astro';
import { SITE } from '../site.config';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="How It Works"
  description="How China Crossroads works: from first inquiry to departure. Transparent 4-step process, no hidden fees, Hong Kong registered company."
>
  {/* 页头 */}
  <section class="bg-ink-900 text-white pt-36 pb-16 sm:pt-44 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <span class="text-vermilion-500 font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">How it works</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl mt-4 leading-[1.1]">From idea to journey,<br />step by step</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-ink-100/70 max-w-2xl">
        No deposits to ask a question. No pressure. Just a clear, transparent process — so you know exactly what happens, what it costs, and what you're paying for.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ===== 4 步流程 ===== */}
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="space-y-12">
      {[
        {
          step: 1,
          title: 'Tell us your idea (free)',
          desc: 'You don\'t need a plan — a rough idea is enough. "Family of four, July, want to see the Great Wall and a robot factory." Send it through our form, WhatsApp, or email.',
          points: ['No payment required', 'Reply within 24 hours', 'Any channel: form, WhatsApp, email, WeChat'],
        },
        {
          step: 2,
          title: 'We design a draft itinerary (free)',
          desc: 'Within 24 hours we reply with a direction: which cities, which ancient sites, which tech projects fit your dates and interests. If you like it, we move to detailed design.',
          points: ['Free draft proposal', 'Honest feasibility check on tech visits', 'Adjustable to your budget'],
        },
        {
          step: 3,
          title: 'Detailed design fee — US$150',
          desc: 'To produce a full day-by-day itinerary with hotels, guides, transfers, confirmed tech-visit availability, and a fixed quote, we charge a US$150 design fee. It\'s fully credited toward your trip if you book within 60 days.',
          points: ['US$150, one-time, non-refundable', 'Fully credited to your trip if booked within 60 days', 'Includes up to 2 rounds of revisions'],
        },
        {
          step: 4,
          title: 'Confirm & travel',
          desc: 'Pay a 40% deposit to confirm (the $150 design fee counts toward it). Final balance is due 45 days before departure. Then you just show up — we handle everything on the ground.',
          points: ['40% deposit to confirm', 'Balance 45 days before departure', '24/7 English support throughout your trip'],
        },
      ].map((item) => (
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[80px_1fr] gap-6">
          <div class="flex sm:flex-col items-center sm:items-start gap-3">
            <div class="font-display text-5xl text-vermilion-500 leading-none">{item.step}</div>
            <div class="hidden sm:block w-12 h-px bg-ink-100"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-ink-900 mb-3">{item.title}</h2>
            <p class="text-ink-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">{item.desc}</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              {item.points.map((p) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-ink-700"><span class="text-vermilion-500">✓</span>{p}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ===== 透明定价 ===== */}
  <section class="bg-ink-50 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="text-vermilion-600 font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Pricing</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink-900 mt-3">Transparent, no surprises</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-ink-500">What you see is what you pay. No hidden fees, no commission shopping stops.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-ink-100 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink-900 mb-2">What's included in every tour</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-500 space-y-2">
            {['Hotels (3-5 star, your choice)', 'All ground transfers & intercity transport', 'English-speaking guide', 'Entrance fees to all sites', 'Most meals', 'Confirmed tech & factory visits'].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-vermilion-500">✓</span>{item}</li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-ink-100 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink-900 mb-2">Not included</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-500 space-y-2">
            {['International flights to/from China', 'Chinese tourist visa (we provide invitation letters)', 'Travel insurance (required)', 'Personal expenses & tips', 'Some free-day meals'].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-ink-400">—</span>{item}</li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-center text-sm text-ink-500">
        Prices on tour pages are <strong>starting prices per person</strong> based on a group of 4 travelers in 4-star hotels.
        Final quote depends on group size, hotel level, and season.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ===== 服务边界声明（增加信任）===== */}
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-ink-900 text-white p-8 sm:p-12">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">What we are — and aren't</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">Being clear about our boundaries is how we earn your trust. Here's exactly where our service starts and ends.</p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-bronze-500 mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">We are</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-white/80 space-y-2">
            {['A Hong Kong registered travel company', 'Travel-side coordinators for your China trip', 'Your on-the-ground fixers for logistics, language, access', 'Curators of ancient + tech experiences'].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-500">◆</span>{item}</li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-vermilion-500 mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">We are not</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-white/80 space-y-2">
            {['A visa or immigration consultancy', 'An investment, legal, or business-brokerage firm', 'A medical or educational service', 'A purchasing agent for goods export'].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-vermilion-500">◆</span>{item}</li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-white/50">
        If you need help in these areas, we'll happily refer you to licensed professionals. We stick to what we do best: travel.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ===== 联系渠道 ===== */}
  <section class="bg-ink-50 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink-900 mb-3">Still have questions?</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-500">Reach us however feels easiest. No deposit, no pressure.</p>
      </div>
      <ContactChannels />
      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" size="lg">Send an inquiry →</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
